  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Get Information about Schools - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_get_information_about_schools">Get Information about Schools</xref>
 is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_register">REGISTER</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_get_information_about_schools">Get Information about Schools</xref>
 (<xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_get_information_about_schools">GIAS</xref>) is a 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_register">REGISTER</xref>
 of all 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_educational_establishment">Educational Establishments</xref>
 in England and is maintained by the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_department_for_education">Department for Education</xref>.        </p>
    <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_get_information_about_schools">Get Information about Schools</xref>
 allows a search of all 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_educational_establishment">Educational Establishments</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_educational_establishment">Educational Establishment</xref>
 Groups and Governors.        </p>
    <p>
For further information on 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_get_information_about_schools">Get Information about Schools</xref>, see the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_department_for_education">Department for Education</xref>
 part of the gov.uk website at: 
              <xref href="https://get-information-schools.service.gov.uk/" scope="external" format="html">Get information about schools</xref>.        </p>
  </div>
